---
title: Mexican-Style Beef Roly Polys with Blistered Green Beans
description: Flour tortillas stuffed with tasty ground beef and smothered in a cheesy sauce … yes please! Get the kids to help with the prep - whether it’s stirring the sauce or rolling up tortillas, they will be sure to enjoy their roly polys if they’ve had a hand in making them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-style-beef-roly-polys-1a4afe6d.jpg
